{"tid":1666621,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣手足請了解伊斯蘭文化(我係教visual culture既)","createTime":"2019-10-21T05:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T05:54:09.000Z","uid":268006,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c50f6232818ae003f0f790b3366479674bb770c","tid":1666621,"uid":268006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:14:09.000Z","msg":"嗱，唔好好似啲無讀通識既黑警咁先得架。<br />\n1. ISIS分分鐘係殺佢地全家果種。讚佢地勇武可以，但千萬唔好提ISIS。<br />\n2. 伊期蘭教係iconoclasm,即係好似基督新教咁唔會畫耶蘇出黎架，又或者好似原始佛教咁，唔會畫佛院出黎，只會以佛印代表佛陀。所以伊斯蘭文化好佢注重書法與幾何圖形。做文宣要靠文字和圖案。唔會畫人、亦唔會畫動物。因為呢個係真主既特權！<br />\n3. 圖案和幾何，可以諗吓九龍清真寺有咩特式。例如門前那棵百年杧果樹，見證住所有香港人，包括伊期蘭教徒既日常生活。可以畫下香港人係大樹下共螎。"},{"pid":"f7d311e15ebe45f75c6607b1fe6e8ae44cde579e","tid":1666621,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa7c6b24437e75bb8a73d002b957cf0433bb087","tid":1666621,"uid":268006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"可以睇吓呢條link <a href=\"https://www.khanacademy.org/humanities/art-islam/beginners-guide-islamic-art/a/arts-of-the-islamic-world\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.khanacademy.org%2Fhumanities%2Fart-islam%2Fbeginners-guide-islamic-art%2Fa%2Farts-of-the-islamic-world&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=e8113f83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.khanacademy.org/humanities/art-islam/beginners-guide-islamic-art/a/arts-of-the-islamic-world</a>"},{"pid":"44bc00a278c37831f07946c22c53341889828329","tid":1666621,"uid":96648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請問連豬會否不尊重？"},{"pid":"f2ae428bbd8036764d